$t[23] = 'Such are the men whom Allah has cursed for He has made them deaf and blinded their sight.';
$t[24] = 'Do they not then earnestly seek to understand the Qur\'an, or are their hearts locked up by them?';
$t[25] = 'Those who turn back as apostates after Guidance was clearly shown to them,- the Evil One has instigated them and busied them up with false hopes.';
$t[26] = 'This, because they said to those who hate what Allah has revealed, &quot;We will obey you in part of (this) matter&quot;; but Allah knows their (inner) secrets.';
